high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter then turn left and walk to the counter to the right of the stove then turn right to face it.
Pick up the clear bowl that's in front of you.
Turn around and walk to the fridge and stand where you can get into the fridge.
Chill the bowl in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the stove and stand in front of it facing it.
Look up and put the bowl in the microwave then close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold bowl in the microwave.

high_descs: Take a right at the fridge and walk to the counter next to the sink.
Pick up the clear container to the right of the stove on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the black fridge.
Put the clear container inside the fridge on the middle shelf, chill it, remove it and close the door.
Turn right and walk to the stove on the right.
Put the chilled container inside the microwave above the stove and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled container in a microwave.

high_descs: Walk to the section of counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the glass bowl off of the counter.
Walk to the fridge that is behind you.
Put the glass bowl in the fridge for a couple seconds and allow it to get cold, then take it out and close the fridge.
Turn right and walk toward the wall, then hang a right and walk over to the oven and look up.
Put the chilled glass bowl in the microwave, then close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled glass bowl in the microwave.
